  ParaTwo="If your current air conditioning unit is outdated or no longer keeping up with the heat, our team can help you upgrade with confidence. We offer full-service HVAC installation in New Port Richey, including system design, energy-efficient unit selection, and precision installation. Our AC systems are built to handle Florida’s humidity and heat while keeping your energy costs under control. We’ll walk you through every step of the process and ensure your new cooling system performs at its best from day one."

  HeaderThree="Local Experts Keeping New Port Richey Homes Cool"
  ParaThree="At Farrell Air Conditioning, we’re proud to be part of the New Port Richey community. Our local technicians understand the unique challenges of Florida’s climate and offer tailored solutions to keep your home comfortable all year long. From seasonal maintenance to emergency HVAC repairs, we deliver honest, high-quality service with no upsells or surprises. Call us today and discover why so many homeowners trust us as their go-to air conditioning contractor in New Port Richey."
/>

  <GoogleReviewsWithoutHeading
  FullNameOne="Maria D"
  FullNameTwo="Jeff C"
